    <title>建立博客系列（二）：next主题相关配置</title>
    <url>/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<p>详细配置可以参考<a href="http://theme-next.iissnan.com/getting-started.html" target="_blank" rel="noopener">官网</a></p>
<h3 id="一、下载"><a href="#一、下载" class="headerlink" title="一、下载"></a>一、下载</h3><p>打开git bash，进入 <code>E:\blog\blog</code>，执行下面的命令，下载速度会有点慢</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git clone https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next themes/next</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>下载完成后，可以看到在themes文件夹下多了一个next文件夹</p>
<h3 id="二、hexo的目录结构"><a href="#二、hexo的目录结构" class="headerlink" title="二、hexo的目录结构"></a>二、hexo的目录结构</h3><blockquote>
<p>_config.yml            //hexo的配置文件 </p>
<p>source</p>
<p>​    _posts                //文章（md文件）所在目录</p>
<p>public                    //根据md文件生成的html文件，执行hexo g生成的文件就在这个目录下</p>
<p>themes</p>
<p>​    landscape</p>
<p>​    next                    //next主题</p>
<p>​        _config.yml    //next主题的配置文件</p>
</blockquote>
<p>这里有两个_config.yml文件，我们把hexo的配置文件称为<strong>站点配置文件</strong>，next主题的配置文件称为<strong>主题配置文件</strong></p>
<p>打开<strong>站点配置文件</strong>，将theme: 项改为next，记住之后所有的配置中冒号后边都先有空格</p>
<p><img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726162208708.png" alt="image-20200726162208708"></p>
<p>运行hexo g， hexo s 打开localhost:4000，看是否成功</p>
<h3 id="三、选择next的风格"><a href="#三、选择next的风格" class="headerlink" title="三、选择next的风格"></a>三、选择next的风格</h3><p>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong>，next提供了四种风格，这里我选择的是Gemini</p>
<p><img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726162346437.png" alt="image-20200726162346437"></p>
<h3 id="四、菜单设置"><a href="#四、菜单设置" class="headerlink" title="四、菜单设置"></a>四、菜单设置</h3><p>打开<strong>主题配置文件</strong></p>
<p><img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726163335226.png" alt="image-20200726163335226"></p>
<p>home是主页，categories是分类，archives是归档，即按时间显示文章，tags是标签，将以上几项的#取消。</p>
<p>打开git bash到<code>E:\blog\blog</code>目录，执行以下代码</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">hexo new page categories</span><br><span class="line">hexo new page tags</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>打开blog\source\categories\index.md文件，添加type</p>
<p><img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726163513556.png" alt="image-20200726163513556"></p>
<p>打开blog\source\tags\index.md文件，添加type</p>
<p><img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726163535408.png" alt="image-20200726163535408"></p>
<h3 id="五、设置头像"><a href="#五、设置头像" class="headerlink" title="五、设置头像"></a>五、设置头像</h3><p>将头像放到 source/images/ 目录下，在<strong>站点配置文件</strong>新增avatar 字段添加路径<img src="/2020/07/26/%E5%BB%BA%E7%AB%8B%E5%8D%9A%E5%AE%A2%E7%B3%BB%E5%88%97%EF%BC%88%E4%BA%8C%EF%BC%89%EF%BC%9Anext%E4%B8%BB%E9%A2%98%E7%9B%B8%E5%85%B3%E9%85%8D%E7%BD%AE/image-20200726163710193.png" alt="image-20200726163710193"></p>
<h3 id="六、添加腾讯公益404页面"><a href="#六、添加腾讯公益404页面" class="headerlink" title="六、添加腾讯公益404页面"></a>六、添加腾讯公益404页面</h3><p>腾讯公益404页面，寻找丢失儿童，让大家一起关注此项公益事业！</p>
<p>如果访问不到资源就会跳转到这个页面</p>
<p>使用方法，新建 404.html 页面，放到主题的 <code>source</code> 目录下，内容如下：</p>
<figure class="highlight html"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="meta">&lt;!DOCTYPE <span class="meta-keyword">HTML</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">"content-type"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"text/html;charset=utf-8;"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">http-equiv</span>=<span class="string">"X-UA-Compatible"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"IE=edge,chrome=1"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"robots"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"all"</span> /&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">meta</span> <span class="attr">name</span>=<span class="string">"robots"</span> <span class="attr">content</span>=<span class="string">"index,follow"</span>/&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">link</span> <span class="attr">rel</span>=<span class="string">"stylesheet"</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/css"</span> <span class="attr">href</span>=<span class="string">"https://qzone.qq.com/gy/404/style/404style.css"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">head</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">type</span>=<span class="string">"text/plain"</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"http://www.qq.com/404/search_children.js"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">          <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span> <span class="attr">homePageUrl</span>=<span class="string">"/"</span></span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">          <span class="attr">homePageName</span>=<span class="string">"回到我的主页"</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://qzone.qq.com/gy/404/data.js"</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="tag">&lt;<span class="name">script</span> <span class="attr">src</span>=<span class="string">"https://qzone.qq.com/gy/404/page.js"</span> <span class="attr">charset</span>=<span class="string">"utf-8"</span>&gt;</span><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">script</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">body</span>&gt;</span></span><br><span class="line"><span class="tag">&lt;/<span class="name">html</span>&gt;</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<h3 id="七、搜索服务"><a href="#七、搜索服务" class="headerlink" title="七、搜索服务"></a>七、搜索服务</h3><p>执行命令</p>
<figure class="highlight shell"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">cnpm install hexo-generator-searchdb --save</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>

<p>在next的配置文件任意位置添加</p>
<figure class="highlight yaml"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line"><span class="attr">search:</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">path:</span> <span class="string">search.xml</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">field:</span> <span class="string">post</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">format:</span> <span class="string">html</span></span><br><span class="line">  <span class="attr">limit:</span> <span class="number">10000</span></span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
]]></content>
